<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 27 at 7:03AM EST  by NWS Pittsburgh</headline>
<description>An area of precipitation is spreading across portions of Western
Pennsylvania. A very brief period of snow, sleet, and freezing
rain is possible for this area between 7am and 10am EST.
Use caution while driving this morning. If you encounter icy
roads, slow down and increase the distance between your vehicle
and those that surround you.</description>
